                  restoration project in Far West Texas.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Designed high-fidelity mock-ups in Figma with a focus on
                  regional aesthetics and responsive design.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Optimized performance through strategic asset loading and
                  caching to achieve 95+ Lighthouse scores.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <section id="danceophile">
